We found that user have trouble understanding the button icons and 3 file stage sections. So, the fail rates here are high and some user couldn't even go through the process to get to the later steps;
https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13174154/29954623-422dc2a4-8ea7-11e7-8669-9ec103daeff2.png
1. Select a file to track  
Correct Action: click [ ] icon in right of that filename 
1st time fail rate: 76.00% , 2nd time fail rate: 44.00%
